                  </dimensions>
                </extent>
                <foliation type="ancient">
                  <p>The folios have been numbered with Coptic arithmetical figures, up to<!-- ADD MISSING "COPTIC" FIGURES -->(i.e. 148, fol.<locus from="146a" to="146a">146 a</locus>).</p>
                </foliation>
                <collation>
                  <p>The quires are 16 in number. They are now signed with letters.</p>
                </collation>
                <condition>
