                  <p>Fol. 7 is of the<date notBefore="0800" notAfter="1000">9th or 10th century</date>.</p>
                </item>
                <item xml:id="addition2" n="2">
                  <locus from="147" to="148"/>
                  <p>Foll. 147 and 148 are<material>paper</material>leaves of the<date notBefore="1200" notAfter="1300">13th century</date>.</p>
                </item>
                <item xml:id="addition3" n="3">
                  <p>Many more lessons are indicated by later hands on the margins.</p>
                </item>
                <item xml:id="addition4" n="4">
                  <p>The larger sections have also been noted on the margins in the<ref target="#b1">Gospel of S. Matthew</ref>, but not, as it would seem, in that of<ref target="#b2">S. Mark</ref>.</p>
                </item>
              </list>
